Package org.universAAL.ri.gateway.proxies.importing

Importing Proxies are components that represent remote components.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ProxyContextSubscriber
    Receives the events the remote BusMember is interested in, and sends the ContextEvents to its representative so it can deliver it to the remote BusMember.
    ProxySCallee
    Represents remote a ServiceCallee, with its subscription parameters synchronized, it is able to get the calls meant for the remote ServiceCallee and send them to the remote proxy which, in time, makes sure a response from the actual ServiceCallee is transmitted back.

Package org.universAAL.ri.gateway.proxies.importing Description

Importing Proxies are components that represent remote components. They contact Exporting proxies in the remote space and communicate with them.
